name: Strawberry Girl
description:
Back in the 90's my boyfriend and I loved Siouxsie and the Banshees, and he said the song Strawberry Girl made him think of me.  Perhaps it is that, or perhaps growing up to cartoons of Strawberry Shortcake, that has convinced me strawberries are the most adorable fruits.  Full of joy, that's for sure!  You cannot take strawberries seriously!  Betty Fvck was generous enough to let me doll her up, and I created this dress and headdress to adorn her in.  She is an amazing drag performer and model living in Helsinki.  Check out all her amazing artistry! 

Model and Makeup Instagram.com/BettyFvck
Headdress, Costume and Photography Bubbles And Frown
